            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指上漲270.21點至13806.7644點，漲幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間25日01:22，深證成指上漲270.21點（或2%），暫報13806.76點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-5.56%</li><li>近 1 月：-7.22%</li><li>近 3 月：-1.68%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.72%</li><li>今年以來：-1.96%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>微信小程式概念領漲+4.84%。其中    東方國信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300166:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300166\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300166-CN</a>)            上漲        9.76%            ;        證通電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002197:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002197\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002197-CN</a>)            上漲        6.66%            ;        吳通控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300292:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300292\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300292-CN</a>)            上漲        3.87%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>F5G概念概念領漲+3.61%。其中    銘普光磁(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002902:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002902\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002902-CN</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        長芯博創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300548:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300548\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300548-CN</a>)            上漲        5.98%            ;        金信諾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300252:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300252\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300252-CN</a>)            上漲        5.35%    。</p></section></main>",
